channel.title: Experienced? Looking for a project? Click here! [NO MORE NEEDED]
channel.description:
I'm working on a survival server, I can basically do everything server sided Looking for a someone who exceeds in client and web development. I'm also looking for someone easy to talk too and .who can help me think of some bomb ideas. I'm looking to have a team of 5 ish people at the most.
I'm looking for our release date to be around march 1st-10th so anyone who wants to join this needs to be dedicated and active!
This is a serious project so expect to be tested and skills heavily examined before being accepted.
[u][b]Application[/b][/u] Name/Nickname: Age: Why would you like to join this project: How would you to contribute to this project: Position wanted: Anything else you want me to know:
[u][b]Available spots[/b][/u] Head developer - Jason (me)
Web developer - Robby
Client developer - (open)
Suggester, and chief economic manager (we'll talk about this position if accepted) - Flame_ - Demonhorn

item.title: Experienced? Looking for a project? Click here! [NO MORE NEEDED]
item.dc:creator: @Ashton51 Ashton51
item.description:
@Ashton51 wrote:

I know you aren’t looking for any server developers but if you change your mind and would like some help with the server sided programming I’m tossing my name into the mix

Name/Nickname:Ash/Ashton
Age:18
Why would you like to join this project:For fun, and I want to return back to the private server scene since Runescape has been completely ruined
How would you to contribute to this project:By making some bomb material for the server
Position wanted:Server Developer
Anything else you want me to know: I am a computer Science Major in my first year of college, I am currently taking my 6th Programming class which is an advanced programming course in Java. I am not a RSPS 1337 server coder, I am a legitimate programmer who knows how to write code in Java. If you have ever heard of OverloadX, I was the Co-Owner and Server developer and we did very well, We were at our peak the most popular RSPS with the most positive votes and a very active player base, over 200 players logged in at a time at any given time of the day. I have been out of the RSPS scene for awhile but want to get back into it for fun since I have free time. If you were to ever consider maybe having an extra developer to create some fun new content for your server then I am your guy
